#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:485
msgid "`ok` (boolean): Whether the exit code is `0`."
msgstr "`ok` (boolean): 終了コードが `0` かどうか。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:485
msgid ""
"`code` (integer|nil): The process exit code. If the process was terminated "
"by a signal, this is `nil`."
msgstr "`code` (integer|nil): プロセス終了コード。シグナルで終了した場合は `nil` です"
"。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:485
msgid "`cmd` (string): Command name used for the execution."
msgstr "`cmd` (string): 実行に使われたコマンド名。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:485
msgid "`cwd` (string): Effective working directory used for the execution."
msgstr "`cwd` (string): 実行に使われた実際の作業ディレクトリ。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:485
msgid "`stdout` (string, optional): Present when `stdout = \"capture\"`."
msgstr "`stdout` (string, 任意): `stdout = \"capture\"` のとき存在します。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:485
msgid "`stderr` (string, optional): Present when `stderr = \"capture\"`."
msgstr "`stderr` (string, 任意): `stderr = \"capture\"` のとき存在します。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:485
msgid ""
"`assert_ok(self)` (function): Raises a structured error when `ok = false`. "
"The error kind is `command_failed`, and the error may include `cmd`, `status`"
", `stderr`, and `cwd`."
msgstr ""
"`assert_ok(self)` (function): `ok = false` のとき構造化エラーを発生 させます"
"。エラー種別は `command_failed` で、`cmd`、`status`、 `stderr`、`cwd` を含む"
"ことがあります。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:496
msgid ""
"The default value of `check` comes from `ptool.config"
"({ run = { check = ... } })`. If not configured, it defaults to `false`. "
"When `check = false`, callers can inspect `ok` themselves or call "
"`res:assert_ok()`."
msgstr ""
"`check` のデフォルト値は `ptool.config({ run = { check = ... } })` から取得さ"
"れます。 未設定ならデフォルトは `false` です。`check = false` のときは、 呼び"
"出し側が自分で `ok` を確認するか `res:assert_ok()` を呼べます。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:499
msgid ""
"When both `check = true` and `retry = true`, `ptool.run` asks whether the "
"failed command should be retried before raising the final error."
msgstr ""
"`check = true` かつ `retry = true` の場合、`ptool.run` は失敗した コマンドを"
"再試行するかどうかを最終エラー前に尋ねます。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:501
msgid ""
"When `check = true`, `ptool.run` raises the same structured `command_failed` "
"error that `res:assert_ok()` raises. Use `ptool.try(...)` if you want to "
"catch and inspect it from Lua."
msgstr ""
"`check = true` の場合、`ptool.run` は `res:assert_ok()` と同じ "
"`command_failed` 構造化エラーを送出します。Lua 側で捕捉して調べたいなら "
"`ptool.try(...)` を使ってください。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/core.md:505
